---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Adrián Domínguez | Fullstack Developer";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img style="border-radius: 50%" width="250" alt="AdrianDC" src="/adrian.jpeg"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Adrián DC</h1>
    <span class="badge">Fullstack Developer</span>
    <h2>About me</h2>
    <p>
    Hi, I'm <strong>Adrián Domínguez Casasola</strong>, a results-driven Fullstack Developer from México. At 
    <a class="link" href="https://waak.dev" target="_blank">[WAAK Dev]</a>, I build scalable web platforms and mobile apps using PHP and React Native, 
    optimizing large-scale client operations with active API integrations and robust cron jobs.
    </p>
    <p>
    Since 2021, I've empowered local businesses by developing professional websites, consistently delivering reliable software solutions. 
    My current focus is on backend development, automating processes with PHP scripts (e.g., invoice generation) and exploring 
    self-hosted solutions on Raspberry Pi.
    </p>
    <div class="center">
        <a href="https://online-cv.adriandomc.com/" target="_blank">
            <button class="btn">Resume (Online)</button>
        </a>
        <a href="/files/Resume_ADC.pdf" target="_blank">
            <button class="btn">Resume (PDF)</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>    
    <div class="skills center">
        
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="PHP" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/php/php-original.svg" />
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="React" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/react/react-original.svg" />
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Cpp" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/cplusplus/cplusplus-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Python" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Raspberry" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/raspberrypi/raspberrypi-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="HTML" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"/>
        <img class="skills__img" width="46" height="46" alt="Git" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>        
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li id="bigli">Programming languages: <strong>PHP</strong>, <strong>C++</strong>, <strong>Python</strong>, <strong>MySQL</strong> and <strong>Javascript</strong>.</li>
        <li id="bigli">Android/iOS app development with <strong>React Native</strong>.
        <li id="bigli">Web development frameworks: <strong>Laravel</strong>, <strong>React</strong>, <strong>Astro</strong> and <strong>Bulma CSS</strong>.</li>
        <li id="bigli">Embedded systems design on <strong>Arduino</strong> and <strong>Raspberry Pi</strong>.</li>
        <li id="bigli">Version control using <strong>Git</strong>.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        I compose and produce music on my psychedelic rock solo project <strong><a class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/@cosmicdinodog" target="_blank">[The Cosmic Dinodog]</a></strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
        I enjoy trekking and going on long walks, as well as practicing martial arts (<strong>Jiujitsu</strong> and <strong>Krav Maga</strong>).
    </p>
    <p>
        Since I was a child, I enjoy reading books, mostly sci-fi, fantasy and pop science. This had an impact on me, which made me curious of 
        language learning:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Spanish (native language)</li>
        <li>Advanced English (B2 certification).</li>
        <li>Basic French (A1 level).</li>
        <li>Japanese and Esperanto (beginner level).</li>
    </ul>
</Layout>

